title: #92Noon Caplan/Leber/Andre Patterson/Jake Wieneke
description: It's PA's last show at this season's training camp. Adam Caplan gives his hot take on who will win the Super Bowl and who's going to be a star this season, regardless. Former MN Viking and current analyst, Ben Leber, weighs in. Defensive Line Coach, Andre Patterson joins the last hour to pay tribute to the late, Aretha Franklin. Kirk Cousins speaks from podium. MN native and Vikings rookie, Jake Wieneke, stops by for the last segment.
